  simp [Set.mem_I, h6] 
```

Now we have `h7 : 0 ∈ (I n : Set ℕ)`. But we also have `h2 : (I n : Set ℕ) = ∅`. 

Substituting `h2` into `h7` gives `0 ∈ ∅`, which is false. This is a contradiction.

```tactics
